Task 1 involved creating a digital literacy awareness infographic using a presentation or design tool such as Canva. The objective was to present key concepts of digital literacy in a visually appealing and easy-to-understand format. The infographic covered topics such as the meaning of digital literacy, useful digital tools for students, safe internet practices, and maintaining a professional online presence.
This task required organizing information effectively, using appropriate visuals, and maintaining clarity in design. It helped in improving creativity, presentation skills, and understanding of how to communicate important information through visual content.
